title: Popular Woodworking - November 2014  USA
description:
Popular Woodworking - November 2014  USA

68 Pages | True PDF | English | 13 MB 

This well produced magazine contains many fascinating features on woodworking, including a huge number of step by step and well illustrated guides to items that you can make yourself, with a particular focus on furniture. Popular Woodworking also includes tips and advice from both readers and the editorial staff and expert tests and reviews of the tools needed to make your creation come to life. A clear, informative read, making it handy for keeping in the workshop or shed.
